text: Quite authentic and very generous portion lean pork basil rice with egg. You can choose how spicy it is and you can add extras. I added a 2nd egg 6$ + 1$ for the extra egg. This a good option at this coffee shop.
Finally found better than Nakhon Affordable thai food! Highly recommend their tomyum soup, basil pork and fresh Thai fried fish!!
Decent stall offering Thai food though prices are at a premium for a coffee shop.

Came by today for a takeaway meal. Ordered Green curry and pineapple fried rice.
The pineapple fried rice was alright and the portion was big. The winner is the green curry. Itâ€™s really flavourful and well done. Good job!
Egg fried rice is cheap and good! They help to cook the duck - ginger and spring onion, taste is good too!
